PrecisRe-appointment of MARCELLE BRISSON, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term effective January 18, 1997 and ending July 17, 1998.
